<item>
            <title>[LU-8540] ib_map_mr_sg() with five arguments</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8540</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Starting in kernel v4.7, ib_map_mr_sg() takes five arguments&lt;br/&gt;
rather than four.  It added an &quot;sg_offset_p&quot; offset pointer&lt;br/&gt;
argument.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;RHEL7.3 also contains this change.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
